Pre-Game Insights: England will be without their regular captain Jos Buttler, who has been injured, and will be led by 28-year-old Phil Salt instead.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Australia began their tour of UK with a record win against Scotland in Edinburgh.
Others: England T20I squad: Phil Salt (c), Jofra Archer, Jacob Bethell, Brydon Carse, Jordan Cox, Sam Curran, Josh Hull, Will Jacks, Liam Livingstone, Saqib Mahmood, Dan Mousley, Jamie Overton, Adil Rashid, Reece Topley, John Turner.
